    Class Description
    AddCommentFragment
    This class defines a fragment used to add comments
    CameraActivity
    This class allows users to take a photo of their QRCode after scanning it
    CaptureAct
    Needed for scanner to work
    EditProfileFragment
    Fragment responsible for displaying the edit profile view and collecting input
    EditProfileFragment.onCompleteListener  
    LeaderboardFragment
    Class for the fragment that shows the Leaderboard and Search Player functionality
    LoginFragment
    Object responsible for prompting user for login info
    MainActivity
    This is the main activity of the app.
    PlaceholderMapFragment
    Fragment responsible for displaying an image as the actual Map functionality has not been implemented
    ProfileFragment
    Fragment responsible for display profile to users
    ProfileFragment.onEditProfileListener  
    QRCode
    This class defines a QR code.
    QRCodeAdapter
    Custom adapter made to implement a custom listview in searched player's profile with name of QR code and its score
    QrCodeImageGenerator
    This class handles QRCode image generation
    QRCodeListItem
    Class to make objects for array adapter used to implement listview in the searched player profile fragment
    QrCodeNameGenerator
    This class handles QR code name generation
    QrCodeOnAddDialog
    Creates a dialog fragment that shows the user the name, score, and picture of the QRCode that they just scanned Also has buttons to save location of QRCode and to take a picture of the QRCode
    QrCodeRepresentative
    This class is implemented by QRCodeImageGenerator and QRCodeNameGenerator
    QrCodeScoreGenerator
    This class handles QRCode score generation
    QRComment
    This class defines a QR code comment
    QRCommentAdapter
    This class defines an adapter for QR comments.
    QRProfileActivity
    The mainActivity of the QR profile.
    SameQRCodeAdapter
    This class defines an adapter for showing the same QR code in QRProfile.
    ScannerFragment
    This class handles QRCode scanning using the zxing-android-embedded library
    ScannerFragment.onCameraClose  
    SearchAdapter
    This class extends ArrayAdapter and implements Filterable.
    SearchedPlayerProfileFragment
    Class for fragment that shows the profile of a player when searched for and clicked in the listview of Leaderboard fragment
    TabManager
    Class responsible for handling tab switching and information passing between tabs
    UserInfo  
    UserInfo.CameraActivity  
    UserListItem
    Class to make objects for array adapter used to implement listview in the leaderboard fragment
    UserProfile
    Model class of user profile info
    WalletCustomList
    WalletCustomList is a class that extends ArrayAdapter to create a custom list view for displaying a list of QRCodes.
    WalletFragment
    This is a class for the fragment that shows the QRCodes in the database, allows us to remove a QRCode, shows the total no.
